value:
I wish we could enjoy the beach
without worryin' about all the
fighting in the world...

I like both the ocean and the
mountains. Either way, ya get
pretty views and lots of critters!

I want to make lunch using the
finest fish from the sea. I'll make
enough for everyone, of course!

The beach would be even better if
Kris were here! I was hopin' to get a
second opinion on this swimsuit.

I just saw Princess Caeda on the
beach. She looks so elegant, even
in a swimsuit.

Hey there! I'm here to give ya
summer greetings from your pal
$Nf!

The beach is real fun! I'm so full of
energy!

Let me know if you get hungry, will
ya? I have some lunches ready to go!

Huh? My legs feel shaky... Was I
having too much fun?

Aww, for me? Thanks! I'll gladly take
a summertime gift!

Heya! I'm Norne. I've really been
lookin' forward to this beach trip!

When I joined the Altean army and
fought around Archanea, I was able
to see beaches from far away.$k$pI always thought it would be nice to
actually go to the beach with friends
and swim in the ocean.$k$pBein' able to realize that dream here
in Askr has made me so happy!$k$pNow that we've all relaxed on the
beach, we can do our best in battle
goin' forward.$k$pWhen all the fighting is done, I hope
I can come to the beach again with
Kris and Lord Marth!
せいっ
I won't lose!
あーっ！
I'll drown!
Try to keep up!
Can't compete with me!
Feel that ocean air!
Splash fight!
Leg...cramp...
Aha
Check me out! Whaddaya think?
Oh! How'd you know I was thirsty? Thank you!
I've actually never been to a beach. This is pretty nice!
Ahh! I'm so relaxed. It's hard to believe we're usually fighting...
There was a real pretty fish over there. It's too bad you missed it.
I wonder what Kris would say about all this...
Oh hey, are you hungry? 'Cause I brought us lunch!
It's so hot today.
Huh? Go where?
I'm on it!
